message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "constitution-overlay: Kustomize-style YAML rule layering with executor-side halt-on-reject for LLM agents"
abstract: "A small, framework-agnostic Python library implementing the constitution + corrections overlay pattern for agentic systems. Provides Kustomize-style merge of YAML rule layers and executor-side enforcement via a halt-on-reject decorator that LLMs cannot bypass."
